(iv)  consult  and  coordinate  with  government  agencies  to  formulate  a  policy 
recommendation and practices that support a sustainable rural financial system in 
the CPEZ; 
(v)  conduct field activities, including field survey, data collection, and meetings; 
(vi)  prepare policy recommendation and relevant sections of the main report in English 
and Chinese; 
(vii) participate and deliver sessions during workshops to disseminate the study findings; 
and 
(viii) perform other related work assigned by the team leader.
